{"General": {"Code": "HAVAS", "Type": "Common Stock", "Name": "HAVAS SA", "Exchange": "AS", "CurrencyCode": "EUR", "CurrencyName": "Euro", "CurrencySymbol": "\u20ac", "CountryName": "Netherlands", "CountryISO": "NL", "OpenFigi": null, "ISIN": "NL0015002AH0", "LEI": null, "PrimaryTicker": "HAV.PA", "CIK": null, "EmployerIdNumber": null, "FiscalYearEnd": "December", "IPODate": null, "InternationalDomestic": null, "Sector": "Communication Services", "Industry": "Advertising Agencies", "GicSector": null, "GicGroup": null, "GicIndustry": null, "GicSubIndustry": null, "Description": "Havas N.V. provides communications and marketing services in France, the United Kingdom, rest of Europe, North America, Latin America, the Asia-Pacific, and Africa. The company offers a range of creative services, such as advertising, brand strategy, business transformation, and digital and social media solutions, as well as public relations and events. It also provides media experiences through media planning and buying, fan engagement, and retail media and e-commerce, as well as data analytics services to optimize client advertising investments. In addition, the company focuses on healthcare and wellness communications, which include providing specialized marketing services to pharmaceutical companies, healthcare providers, and wellness brands. Further, it offers business consultancy, brand consultancy and design, public affairs and corporate communications, brand partnership and sponsorship, production and content, and customer experience services. The company serves healthcare and wellness, finance, consumer goods, food and beverages, technology, media and telecom, industry and services, automotive, retail, travel, entertainment, and other industries. Havas N.V. was founded in 1835 and is headquartered in Puteaux, France.", "Address": "29-30, quai de Dion-Bouton, Puteaux, France, 92800", "AddressData": {"Street": "29-30, quai de Dion-Bouton", "City": "Puteaux", "Country": "France", "ZIP":